text:
Great! Thanks to you, I managed to take
a bunch of photos during the training camp!

...That being said,
I'm not sure if they turned out well.
Well, considering it's a disposable camera.

But,
I believe I got some good shots.
After all, there fantastic subjects to photograph!

Isn't saying that because Yuika enjoyed herself
and tried her best a valid reason?

...It's not that it's not a valid reason, but rather,
it feels a bit cheesy, doesn't it?
